OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FJack Fitzwater tells ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry's Ross Arnott about his
OL,9,Fulcerative colitis diagnosis and why
OL,10,Fhe hid it for so long.
OL,12,FAn footballer has said that opening up
OL,13,Fabout his recent ulcerative colitis
OL,14,Fdiagnosis has helped him come to terms
OL,15,Fwith his condition.
OL,17,FJack Fitzwater, who is 26, is living
OL,18,Fwith ulcerative colitis, a condition
OL,19,Fwhich affects your digestive system
OL,20,Fand bowels.
