OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe footballer says that at its worst,
OL,8,Fhe was forced to go to the toilet more
OL,9,Fthan 30 times a day and even
OL,10,Fconsidered retirement.
OL,12,FJack told ITV News West Country he
OL,13,Finitially hid his symptoms from his
OL,14,Fteammates, friends and family, because
OL,15,Fhe didn't want it to be seen as a
OL,16,F"weakness".
OL,18,FHe said: "I think it was just an
OL,19,Funcomfortable subject - until you
OL,20,Fstart speaking about it.
