OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"I was probably hiding it from people
OL,8,Fin football. I didn't want it to be
OL,9,Fseen as 'he won't play today because
OL,10,Fhe's got this' or that kind of thing."
OL,12,FJack is one of around 300,000 people
OL,13,Faffected by ulcerative colitis in the
OL,14,FUK, but said he'd never heard of the
OL,15,Fcondition before being diagnosed.
OL,17,FThe main symptoms include recurring
OL,18,Fdiarrhoea, as well as stomach pain and
OL,19,Fneeding to go to the toilet regularly.
