OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAt its worst, Jack said he was forced
OL,8,Fto go to the bathroom more than 30
OL,9,Ftimes a day.
OL,11,F"I was waking up, toilet. Middle of
OL,12,Fthe night, toilet. General moodiness
OL,13,Fand fatigue," he said.
OL,15,F"I went to Ibiza with my family and it
OL,16,Fwas just constantly going to the
OL,17,Ftoilet. I didn't want to wake up my
OL,18,Fgirlfriend or it be awkward in and
OL,19,Faround the hotel - so I'd be getting
OL,20,Fup at 3 or 4am."
