OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FHe said there were times when he
OL,8,Fthought about retiring as a
OL,9,Ffootballer, but "the worst thing (he)
OL,10,Fprobably did was hide it for so long."
OL,12,F"I was thinking there's no chance I
OL,13,Fcan train or play. It's a nightmare.
OL,14,FThere were definitely times when I
OL,15,Fthought 'I might have to give this up'
OL,16,Flast summer," he explained.
