OL,3,CFootballer Jack Fitzwater on why he
OL,4,Cconsidered retiring after health
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"The best thing I did was tell people
OL,8,Fabout my diagnosis. Now it's out in
OL,9,Fthe open, I'm training well, I'm
OL,10,Fplaying well, I'm back in the team,"
OL,11,Fhe added.
